sellerAgent.name: Fire Family Real Estate - Team Nunez

data.description: This 4 bed beauty boasts tremendous natural light throughout and is a mere 19 minutes to the beach! Features include Plantation Shutters, Newer Windows, Newer Roof, Recently Painted, newer AC Unit and so much more! Full Bed & full Bath downstairs! Oversized Master Bed is upstairs w/ dual closets, dual sinks + soaking tub with a remodeled separate shower + skylights. NO HOA & NO MELLO ROOS! The kitchen opens up to the living room and has a breakfast nook area with great views to the beautifully landscaped & spacious yard. Backyard is an Entertainers paradise with newly laid pavers and space abound! Ideally located in a desirable area near excellent schools, parks, shopping, restaurants +more!***Home Priced within a range of $899,999-$924,999***
